      <p><strong>Address:</strong> 1 Rochor Canal Road, #05-01 Sim Lim Square</p>
      <p><strong>Services:</strong> Trade-in and sales of pre-owned/demo/display and refurbished laptops and other portable electronic devices such as smartphones and tablets.</p>
      <p><strong>Contact:</strong> <a href="https://www.nea.gov.sg/our-services/waste-management/3r-programmes-and-resources/recycling-collection-points" target="_blank">PC Dreams</a></p>
      <p><strong>Distance:</strong> ~10 km</p>
    </div>
    <div class="card" data-category="Repair">
      <h2>The Salvation Army - Tanglin Donation Booth</h2>
      <p><strong>Address:</strong> 356 Tanglin Road, Singapore 247674</p>
      <p><strong>Services:</strong> Accepts donations of furniture, clothing, and household goods. Items in good condition may be repaired and sold in their thrift stores.</p>
      <p><strong>Contact:</strong> <a href="https://styledegree.sg/ultimate-list-of-places-to-donate-old-clothes-items-in-singapore/" target="_blank">The Salvation Army</a></p>
